28571428571866, \"text\": \"Gayton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\"}, {\"begin\": 849, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"score\": 0.9999999248480008, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chauke\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking in apress conferenceat the Market Theatre in Johannesburg on Thursday, 17 October, Gayton McKenzie sought to clear up any confusion about his travel expenses.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 925, \"end\": 939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Market_Theatre_(Johannesburg)\", \"score\": 0.9999967264078727, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Market Theatre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Market_Theatre_(Johannesburg)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Market_Theatre_(Johannesburg)\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 955, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.466972944213082e-13, \"text\": \"Johannesburg\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Johannesburg\"}, {\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gayton McKenzie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this week, Gayton tweeted that his trip to the Paris Olympics was for dual purposes.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1077, \"end\": 1083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"score\": 0.476338266024737, \"rank\": 0.7028571428571866, \"text\": \"Gayton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was to watch the Opening Ceremony and to attend several government meetings.\", \"from\": 1151, \"to\": 1232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"score\": 0.9999973894007296, \"rank\": 2.518505114423035e-06, \"text\": \"Opening Ceremony\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Opening_ceremony\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Addressing the media, Gayton said: \\\"I have done absolutely nothing wrong.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"score\": 0.476338266024737, \"rank\": 0.7028571428571866, \"text\": \"Gayton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am as transparent as possible.\\\"\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1341, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The minister went on to explain that he chose a \\\"cheaper\\\" four-star accommodation instead of a five-star one.\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also explained that prices were abnormally high because of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You can not compare Euros with Rands.\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1568, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our currency is not that strong,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1611, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gayton shadily added: \\\"Do not say I went for a joyride, and do not compare me to Mama Joy.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1703, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1613, \"end\": 1619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"score\": 0.476338266024737, \"rank\": 0.7028571428571866, \"text\": \"Gayton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not a super fan; I am the Minister of Sports, Art and Culture\\\".\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On her X account, Mama Joy also appeared to throw shade at Gayton McKenzie, who was being questioned over his travel expenses.\", \"from\": 1774, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1833, \"end\": 1848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gayton McKenzie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton_McKenzie\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 50-year-old sports fan posted a screenshot of a journalist who wanted to know if she believed the minister was \\\"two-faced\\\" over allegations he misused public funds.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's unclear if she has responded.\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chauke also reposted a tweet by EFF member Sinawo Thambo who had filed a complaint about Gayton with the Public Prosecutor.\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2108, \"end\": 2114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"score\": 0.9999999248480008, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chauke\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\"}, {\"begin\": 2140, \"end\": 2143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_Frontier_Foundation\", \"score\": 0.9999999993792699, \"rank\": 6.207716942110031e-10, \"text\": \"EFF\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_Frontier_Foundation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Electronic_Frontier_Foundation\"}, {\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"score\": 0.476338266024737, \"rank\": 0.7028571428571866, \"text\": \"Gayton\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\"}, {\"begin\": 2213, \"end\": 2230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"score\": 0.9997861427969967, \"rank\": 0.00021390294772341345, \"text\": \"Public Prosecutor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Prosecutor\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thambo's tweet referencing the minister read: \\\"Having Gayton Mckenzie as a Minister feels like being robbed at knifepoint every day.\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2365, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When you try to heal, the criminal comes and promises to donate his salary.\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2441, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When you turn the other side, the criminal promises to reimburse athletes who paid their own way to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2557, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When you think you are recovering, the criminal spends R400k on ground transport and R215k on flights.\\\"\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Mama Joy also retweeted another shady tweet about Gayton that read: \\\"@joychauke5 was sidelined by the minister for him to enjoy those benefits alone.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2813, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2714, \"end\": 2720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gayton,_Northamptonshire\", \"score\": 0.476338266024737, \"rank\": 0.7028571428571866, \"text\": \"Gayton\", \"